Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Mt. Tamalpais
Description: A mountain in Nor Cal with miles of beautiful open space offering fun for hikers and bikers alike

Name: Ring Mountain
Description: a small quiet open area in Marin County with a wooden bench to sit on and look at breathtaking views of the SF Bay Area

Name: Rincon Point
Description: World class surf spot and a great beach to lie out on and get a tan and watch the surfers

Name: Oracle Park
Description: Home of the SF Giants its is a modern baseball park next to the water, perfect for a summer night ball game

Name: Chateau Montelena
Description: A winery in Napa Valley offering wine tasting on their grounds with vineyards and koy fish ponds
